                            </ListItem>
                            <ListItem>
                                <Paragraph x:Name="para6" FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="15">Ribbon Bar Modes - LargeButton mode and SmallButton mode.</Paragraph>
                            </ListItem>
                            <ListItem>
                                <Paragraph x:Name="para7" FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="15">Ribbon has a custom implementation of button control as RibbonButton.</Paragraph>
                            </ListItem>
                            <ListItem>
                                <Paragraph x:Name="para9" FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="15">Can minimize/maximize the ribbon.</Paragraph>
                            </ListItem>
                            <ListItem>
                                <Paragraph x:Name="para10" FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="15">Keyboard navigation simplified through Key Tip (super accelerator support).</Paragraph>
                            </ListItem>
                            <ListItem>
